+++++Rationale: Currently half the training time is spent in LR cooldown (WARMDOWN_RATIO=0.5). This is aggressive and means the model spends only 50% of training at peak learning rate. Reducing to 0.35 gives 65% of training at peak LR, allowing more learning before cooldown begins. The final LR still reaches 0 (FINAL_LR_FRAC=0.0) so convergence is preserved, but more tokens are processed at high LR, which should lower val_bpb.
